---
import DocLayout from '../layouts/DocLayout.astro';
---
<DocLayout title="Compliance — Autional Docs">
<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Compliance Guide</h1>
<p class="mb-6 text-neutral-600">Autional provides tooling and data models for 8 compliance frameworks. Compliance certification is the responsibility of the deploying organization.</p>
<h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 mt-8">Supported Frameworks</h2>
<table class="w-full text-sm mb-6 border-collapse"><thead><tr class="border-b border-neutral-200"><th class="text-left font-medium py-2 px-2">Framework</th><th class="text-left font-medium py-2 px-2">Autional Tooling</th></tr></thead><tbody>
<tr class="border-b border-neutral-100"><td class="py-2 px-2">GDPR</td><td class="py-2 px-2">DSAR automation, 7-service erasure orchestration, consent management</td></tr>
<tr class="border-b border-neutral-100"><td class="py-2 px-2">SOC 2</td><td class="py-2 px-2">Audit trail, access controls, monitoring, incident management</td></tr>
<tr class="border-b border-neutral-100"><td class="py-2 px-2">ISO 27001</td><td class="py-2 px-2">ISMS controls, risk assessment, asset management</td></tr>
<tr class="border-b border-neutral-100"><td class="py-2 px-2">PCI DSS</td><td class="py-2 px-2">Cardholder data controls, access logging, encryption at rest</td></tr>
<tr class="border-b border-neutral-100"><td class="py-2 px-2">HIPAA</td><td class="py-2 px-2">PHI access controls, audit trails, breach notification</td></tr>
<tr class="border-b border-neutral-100"><td class="py-2 px-2">Dengbao 2.0</td><td class="py-2 px-2">Chinese national standard security controls, SM crypto</td></tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 mt-8">Key Compliance Features</h2>
<h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 mt-6">Hash-Chain Audit Logs</h3>
<p class="mb-4 text-neutral-600">Every authentication event is recorded in a Merkle hash chain. The integrity of the chain can be cryptographically verified at any time. This provides tamper-proof evidence for auditors.</p>
<h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 mt-6">Data Retention</h3>
<p class="mb-4 text-neutral-600">Configurable retention policies per data type. Schedule-based archival and cleanup jobs. Audit logs can be retained indefinitely for compliance requirements.</p>
<h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 mt-6">Data Classification</h3>
<p class="mb-4 text-neutral-600">4 classification levels: Public, Internal, Confidential, Restricted. Data classification is enforced at the API and storage layers.</p>
<h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 mt-6">Cross-Border Transfers</h3>
<p class="mb-4 text-neutral-600">GDPR-compliant cross-border data transfer assessment management. Document legal bases, safeguards, and transfer impact assessments.</p>
<div class="rounded-xl bg-amber-50 dark:bg-amber-900/10 border border-amber-200 dark:border-amber-900/20 p-6 mt-8">
<h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Compliance Disclaimer</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">The tooling described above provides the technical foundation for compliance. Achieving certification requires organization-specific policies, controls, and third-party audits. Autional does not guarantee compliance certification through platform features alone.</p></div>
</DocLayout>
